### Business Logic Layer
* Express with Prisma for API gateway and database interaction
	+ Implement RESTful APIs using Express routers
	+ Utilize Prisma's ORM capabilities for type-safe database queries

### Data Storage Layer
* Postgres as primary database with proper schema design
	+ Define tables with descriptive names and relationships
	+ Implement database transactions for atomicity and consistency

