## API Contract Enhancements {#api-contract-enhancements}
Add documentation, example responses, and request bodies to each endpoint:
```
GET    /api/resource
  * Returns list of resources with pagination (max 20 pages)
  * Example response: `[{"id": 1, "name": "Resource 1"}, ...]`

POST   /api/resource
  * Creates a new resource with the provided data
  * Request body: `{"id": null, "name": "New Resource"}`
  * Example response: `{ "id": 10, "name": "New Resource" }`

GET    /api/resource/{id}
  * Returns resource details by ID
  * Example response: `[{"id": 1, "name": "Resource 1"}, ...]`
```

